  "mainText": "Video Pens Games Our way of life Inspirational box Sample kits go to maxema.com en Italiano English Video Pens Games Our way of life Inspirational box Sample kits Order go to maxema.com en Italiano English WATCH THE VIDEO WATCH THE VIDEO Design embraces sustainability Discover the pleasure of sustainable writing with our recycled plastic pens. Also available in two models with antibacterial additive. Icon Pure in recycled plastic - model IC8-MATT RE Flow Pure in recycled plastic - models F2P-MATT CB RE and F2P-MATT RE Dot in recycled plastic - models D1-MATT CB RE and D1-MATT RE Zink in recycled plastic - models Z1-CB RE and Z1-C RE Pixel in recycled plastic - models PX40-MATT CB RE and PX40-MATT RE Bay in recycled plastic - model B500-MATT RE Icon pure Icon Pure in recycled plastic - model IC8-MATT RE Flow Pure Flow Pure in recycled plastic - models F2P-MATT CB RE and F2P-MATT RE Dot Dot in recycled plastic - models D1-MATT CB RE and D1-MATT RE Zink Zink in recycled plastic - models Z1-CB RE and Z1-C RE Pixel Pixel in recycled plastic - models PX40-MATT CB RE and PX40-MATT RE Bay Bay in recycled plastic - model B500-MATT RE Tag Green Recycled Antibacterial Icon Green Recycled Antibacterial The earth is full of shades Discover the eight colors inspired by nature 06 ICE 10 CLOUD 58 GRAPHITE 87 MUD 76 DESERT 19 FOREST 21 ABYSS 07 ONYX Ice Cloud Graphite Onyx Mud Desert Forest Abyss All models can be made of recycled plastic on request. For orders higher than 10,000 pcs. Choose your favourite Recycled plastic lovers The plastic in our pens is 100% post-consumer WEEE (Waste Electrical and Electronic Equipment), and is certified and compliant with RoHS and REACH. A long-lasting pen loves nature Our pens are designed to last as long as possible. Using our refills you can write up to 4 km with just one pen. One life is too short We use materials that are not only recycled, but also recyclable. The sustainable mission of our pens continues even after they hav